          "role": "assistant",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "You can use asyncio.wait_for() or asyncio.timeout() (Python 3.11+):\n\n```python\n# asyncio.wait_for raises asyncio.TimeoutError after the deadline\ntry:\n    result = await asyncio.wait_for(some_coroutine(), timeout=5.0)\nexcept asyncio.TimeoutError:\n    print('timed out')\n\n# asyncio.timeout context manager (3.11+)\nasync with asyncio.timeout(5.0):\n    result = await some_coroutine()\n```"
            }
